  ORD->>IGW: Create charge (REST)
  IGW->>CB: Create charge (API)
  CB-->>IGW: Webhook (payment confirmed)
  IGW->>IGW: Verify HMAC signature
  IGW-->>K: payment.completed (crypto)
  K-->>ORD: payment.completed
  ORD-->>K: order.completed
```

